WORKFLOW.DESCRIPTION: This mapping ports the CollisionTrans data from HQSQLCOLLTRP(alias to production) to the StagingCollisionDataMart database with the exception of Colli_Dtl_Info, Colli_Unit, Comrcl_Carr, MV_Drvr, and MV_Unit. The Colli_Dtl_Info, Colli_Unit and Comrcl_Carr tables have to be ported through a stored procedure because of Informatica's inability to handle bit fields correctly. The MV_Drvr, and MV_Unit tables must be ported by stored procedure because we are putting NULLs in the encrypted fields.
WORKFLOW.NAME: LoadStagingCollisionDatamart
